name: Scorpion
desc:
You'd better check your pockets.
These guys like to hide.

name: Momma Boar
desc:
It follows you around.
No matter what you do.

name: Tired Zombie
desc:
Usually spreads some disease.
Don't stand too close.

name: Eight-legged Menace
desc:
Always appears out of nowhere.
A little bit more scary at night.

name: Silverback Gorilla
desc:
Be careful around this one!
Especially about its "Unga Bunga".

name: Swamp Gator
desc:
So it wasn't a floating log after all.
This is making you a little uncomfortable.

name: Gator Duo
desc:
It is getting out of hand.
Now there are two of them.

name: Nimble Knight
desc:
They used to be an adventurer like you.
Then they took an arrow to the knee.

name: Fire Elemental
desc:
It seems to be sentient.
Protect your elder scrolls.

name: Floating Germs
desc:
Feels uncomfortable on your skin.
And now it's too late to be sorry.

name: Swarm of Flies
desc:
No matter what you do.
You stay totally surrounded.

name: Ring of Love
desc:
Keeps your heart warm.
Could bring back lost memories.

name: Prosthetic Arm
desc:
Could this be a weapon?
There's only one way to find out.

name: Ancient Taco
desc:
Looks fresh and tasty.
What could go wrong?

name: Mysterious Box
desc:
You wonder what's inside?
There's only one way to find out.
